reason: To get a better view of the full height of the target building from ground to roof, I will move to the front-left node which is 10 meters away, as this position should provide a more complete perspective of the structure.

Moving back to the previous node (10 meters away) will return me to the position where I was initially facing the target building's North-East direction, allowing me to observe its structure for height estimation.
